>\n<br />\n我理解美金cash account負錢就等於借咗ib錢。咁如果我負錢嘅時候，想喺ib唱美金，再轉去其他戶口例如charles schwab，咁會唔會我喺ib一轉美金，都未轉走，佢就自動幫我用咗嚟還ib孖展㗎??定係要另外揀掣先會settle 啲 margin 架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:53:37.000Z","msg":"前題係（1）條債唔default及（2）持有期內個價唔會跌到你比人斬倉"},{"pid":"3e8d8f98bfc444dc150d329b284e9ce2e80a231a","tid":2462305,"uid":54884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:54:34.000Z","msg":"上年3月你就死哂"},{"pid":"2c3e84400a46095655234ba6d308ca078e354824","tid":2462305,"uid":352639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ad84cdcea6a1b01616e87bab817d6e299107bb8b","tid":2462305,"uid":67749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:34:39.000Z","msg":"你講嘅YouTuber 係股壇劉玄德呢條財演？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:55:54.000Z","msg":"係啊，財演黎㗎咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7baa0807c6726a09dc988fd62379d54a62a503ca","tid":2462305,"uid":352639,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"97a2efc80c95ccf57d2ec9cf828234d0ff4ce490","tid":2462305,"uid":260744,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:41:49.000Z","msg":"唔打靶咪好搵囉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:57:23.000Z","msg":"請問咩係打靶? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ncall 返啲callable 嘅債券?"},{"pid":"9ce0495303a79d466a99a32b9100cdf38570a71a","tid":2462305,"uid":352639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6e1fc4a8a199352debc20db306035461ee9acbf","tid":2462305,"uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:46:22.000Z","msg":"即係咁，做呢種trade，某程度上你係做銀行角色做套息活動，借短貸長。銀行貸款部面對嘅問題你都會面對。<br />\n<br />\n但當出現問題時，你是否有能力處理先係問題關鍵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:04:16.000Z","msg":"冇知識、冇經驗，所以做定功課諗定曬先敢再考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁大家有咩建議? 另外有個youtuber rain is here 話點都唔借錢，係咪比較好?<br />\n<br />\n但而家息口咁低，幾乎減無可減，即係未來只有加息，長遠債價只會有跌冇升，咁就算唔借錢，就咁買債好似都好高風險，但唔通個倉唔擺債券？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b251cb45ead177ed5774a18f898e9c5090631e2d","tid":2462305,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7baa0807c6726a09dc988fd62379d54a62a503ca","tid":2462305,"uid":352639,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"97a2efc80c95ccf57d2ec9cf828234d0ff4ce490","tid":2462305,"uid":260744,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:41:49.000Z","msg":"唔打靶咪好搵囉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:57:23.000Z","msg":"請問咩係打靶? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ncall 返啲callable 嘅債券?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:05:50.000Z","msg":"因為攞債抵壓做margin，債價跌要補錢，仲要債價係個莊開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad466ed34dcea6aeff976490f40b7cfd435fdf59","tid":2462305,"uid":40684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bce13f5e7094d01f6a0290074acbded06c03d5a5","tid":2462305,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:32:19.000Z","msg":"問YouTuber 皮老闆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:07:44.000Z","msg":"變左收皮老闆"},{"pid":"84b42b289b6e1b75f4c33f1b57ca176aa149c9fa","tid":2462305,"uid":352639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"355d2fa767351b1d35bc09c40c663259574ed7f3","tid":2462305,"uid":61510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"131a39a505f028fc93155595f9df3603b3e141cb","tid":2462305,"uid":352639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:25:52.000Z","msg":"小弟新手未入市，做緊功課，請教下大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲youtuber，成日話槓桿買債好搵，ib又低息，咁啊叔我舉個例大家傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋晚search 左有隻債咁樣:<br />\n<br />\n信貸評級: a-<br />\ncoupon: 8.x%<br />\nmaturity: 十幾廿年後<br />\nprice: 150<br />\nyield to maturity: 4.5%<br />\n<br />\n咁假如我槓桿比 1:2, 買100蚊借200蚊, ytm 就泵大到 4.5% x 3 = 13.5%<br />\n<br />\n減去ib margin 1.5% 息, 就 13.5% - 3% = 10.5%<br />\n<br />\n咁睇落都唔錯吖，但我就唔明喇:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>問題1</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n買完之後點部署? 我每月份糧suppose 有部份會繼續買債，而買左果條債都有息收，咁暫時諗到2個options<br />\n<br />\nOption 1:<br />\n出左嘅糧就繼續買新債，當都係同上面個條一樣1:2 margin, 10.5% ytm。而債券收息就用黎還margin，或者跟&quot;現金流為王&quot;咁做，買reits用reits嘅息還margin, 總之就用黎還錢。<br />\n<br />\n但個問題就係 (i) ytm個數好似計埋interest reinvestment. 如果息口唔買返落條債道，其實當初ytm根本冇4.5%; (ii) 個portfolio嘅債券倉會冇左複利息效果(因為個成長，即債息，用左黎還錢); (iii) 成個債券倉ytm持續下降，因為還左少少錢之後，margin比由 1:2 變成 1:1.99x, 而且日後keep住還，會keep住跌。<br />\n<br />\noption 2:<br />\n唔還錢，每月新資金，及債息，都用黎買新債，當一樣係ytm 4.5%, 1:2 margin, 即total ytm 同上係10.5%<br />\n<br />\noption 2 個問題係加息<br />\n<br />\n我新手心諗, 如果ib margin係浮息，咁加息果時，如果ib margin 加到3% 咁個 yield 會由10.5% 跌到得7.5% 左右。<br />\n<br />\n而最慘係債價會因為加息而跌，咁咪好易call margin?<br />\n<br />\n而仲有個問題就係當唔加息喇，但個price (即150) 會隨年期跌到 par value, 即跌到maturity 果時100。跌咁多其實係咪姐係就算唔加息，都終有一日會call margin?? (所以要預備好多保證金?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以有youtuber 講槓桿債話 &quot;買債係先苦後甜, 揀好左坐喺度收息就得&quot;. 其實option 1 就可能得，但回報遠比想像中少，而option 2 更加驚心，唔係坐喺度就得。<br />\n<br />\n又有話&quot;債券最終會返到100蚊，中間升跌唔洗理佢&quot;, 其實係講緊保證金要好夠? 因為返100=跌左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以總結槓桿債係極度息口敏感，而且最好買果陣低過par value (e.g. 9x.xx) 等佢慢慢到期升到par (i.e.100). 所以而家咁低息買債=差嘅出手? 而家息口已經減無可減咁滯，一旦加息，債價跌就損曬手。<br />\n<br />\n我有冇搞錯啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>問題2</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n問題2更加新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我理解美金cash account負錢就等於借咗ib錢。咁如果我負錢嘅時候，想喺ib唱美金，再轉去其他戶口例如charles schwab，咁會唔會我喺ib一轉美金，都未轉走，佢就自動幫我用咗嚟還ib孖展㗎??定係要另外揀掣先會settle 啲 margin 架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:53:37.000Z","msg":"前題係（1）條債唔default及（2）持有期內個價唔會跌到你比人斬倉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:09:06.000Z","msg":"default 問題都算, 最多買giant company降低風險<br />\n<br />\n跌價先大疑惑，因為加息會跌，但而家咁低息，所以長遠只有加，好難減到負息率，即係多數都跌價，就算唔跌價都唔會升。<br />\n<br />\n就算當唔加息，條債價會逐漸回返到par value 100, 咁姐係必跌??? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed41d2cdca7d4f96f932e22e2eba951d11bfcbe","tid":2462305,"uid":393727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ce0495303a79d466a99a32b9100cdf38570a71a","tid":2462305,"uid":352639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"